"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640317909,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"FsGlP6n0VfDnSJfDLFAq81e6f3hMgHDQjtimJY3OhV8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xb60154b28F6158362AAf37623720C3DE6e1Dd131\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"TqmbN3k7TzyJwJO4c8slAJ9D79Z_Hg2__9t1he30zGk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qx-Rz8x1NY43RUjdzGNQFnibmGB3eRm87OydLSqw3jY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"d4BkJadip0alKKgaABnMjsG8Px3DKCGQCNfmJuLPMV5cC_jXH3Ghu2_Fa1DMA5SrL8Qe_QGkkU0Fxqclv7W1cg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x1b66706911eff50311bb330519bf506d7b42b5b478d3966c0afb814da5d627ea55cac7917430cdbe3419827ebd94a06e041837100c202445d3e99dfa12c18d651b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"TqmbN3k7TzyJwJO4c8slAJ9D79Z_Hg2__9t1he30zGk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qx-Rz8x1NY43RUjdzGNQFnibmGB3eRm87OydLSqw3jY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi